window.bookSummaryJSON = "Rob, a professional debunker, is watching yet another performance by a supposed psychic. But as she calls forth the spirit entity known as Isus, another voice suddenly interrupts. And this one is so unexpected and so real, even the hardened skeptic finds he can't help but believe. <p>This engaging, humorous tale of the beyond won a Hugo Award for Best Novella.</p>"; 
